v 2.2.0
  - Added Piwik analytics.
  - Reorganised items in the configuration menu

v 2.1.0
  - Added the Material theme (SirQuackTheDuck)

v 2.0.2
  - Fixed watched videos not being marked on reload.

v 2.0.1
  - Fixed videos not showing up when using YTAPI2 (off by one)
  - Fixed configuration export

v 2.0.0
  - Use asynchronous XMLHttpRequests, improving loading speed
  - Added a part of the video description to video tooltips
  - Added a config option to control the amount of videos loaded
  - Channels can now be added by name, ID and URL
  - Fixed a few graphical quirks
  - Added support for YouTube Native playback
  - Added support for YouTube API V3
  - Drop native playback using ViewTube. Use YouTube HTML5 instead.
  - Added an option to disable the alternative horizontal scrolling

v 1.0.4
  - Show hours and minutes on recent videos

v 1.0.3
  - Remove theme comments
  - The browser is now in charge of selecting the proper video format

v 1.0.2
  - Dropped the Mickeysoft theme
  - Removed the text-shadow from the Dusk theme
  - Fixed some crappy CSS
  - Update ViewTube module

v 1.0.1
  - Fixed channel titles being displayed incorrectly in Chromium

v 1.0
  - Inital release
  - Subscribe to YouTube channels without the need for a Google+ account
